  | publisher =
  | date =
  | url =http://www.tcnj.edu/~kpearson/Mumia/part1.htm
  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =}}
</ref>, taking appointment as its chapter Lieutenant Minister of Information exercising a responsibility for authoring propaganda and news communications.<ref>{{cite web
  | last =
  | first =
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
  | title =Danielfaulkner.com summary of case facts
