  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =  }}</ref> He spent the winter of 1969 in [[New York City|New York]] and the spring of 1970 in [[Oakland, California|Oakland]], living and working with BPP comrades in those cities.<ref>{{cite web
  | last =Burroughs 
  | first =Todd Steven 
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
  | title =Ready to Party: Mumia Abu-Jamal and the Black Panther Party (Part 2)
  | work =
  | publisher =
