  | url =http://www.tcnj.edu/~kpearson/Mumia/part2.htm
  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =  }}</ref> He was a Party member for the period from May 1969 until October 1970, and was subject to some degree of [[FBI]] [[COINTELPRO]] [[surveillance]] during that time and afterwards continuing through until about 1974.<ref>{{cite web
  | last =Burroughs
  | first =Todd Steven
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
  | title =Ready to Party: Mumia Abu-Jamal and the Black Panther Party (Part 3)
