  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =  }}</ref>

Through the 1970s, he fathered Lateefa and Mazi, his youngest child. His first marriage, to Biba when he was aged 19, proved to be short-lived.<ref>{{cite web
  | last =
  | first =
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
  | title =The Religious Affiliation of 
Mumia Abu-Jamal
  | work =
