  | format =
  | doi =
  | accessdate =  }}</ref> By 1975 he was pursuing a vocation in radio newscasting, first at [[Temple University]]'s [[WRTI]] and then at commercial enterprises.<ref>{{cite web
  | last =Kissinger
  | first =C. Clark 
  | authorlink =
  | coauthors =
