  | accessdate =  }}</ref> He was also employed for brief periods at radio station [[WPEN]].<ref>ibid.</ref> From 1979 he worked at [[WHYY-FM|WUHY]] public radio station until 1981 when he was asked to submit his resignation in a dispute over reporting the news objectively.<ref>{{cite news 
  | last =
  | first =
