</ref> and [[Amnesty International]]<ref>{{cite press release
  | title =USA: Mumia Abu-Jamal -- Amnesty International calls for retrial
  | publisher =Amnesty International
  | date = February 17, 2000 
  | url =http://web.amnesty.org/library/Index/engAMR510202000
  | accessdate =  }}
</ref>; and the persistence of activist cells variously known as chapters of the [http://www.freemumia.org ''Free Mumia Coalition''] and the [http://www.mumia.org ''International Concerned Family and Friends of Mumia Abu-Jamal''].

